This template is based on code written by yhirose for the GitHub repository
https://github.com/yhirose/cpp-peglib. Modifications by SociableFish include:
* Making the project use include as an include path instead of the project root
* Removing the actual PEG parser library and leaving include/yourlib.h instead
* Simplifying CMakeLists.txt to use only one option, YOURLIB_BUILD_TESTS
* Simplifying test/CMakeLists.txt to use a single file, test.cpp

